questions.title: Are you a pupper, doggo, or maybe even a woofer, perhaps?
questions.body: Great question, anon! I am just a little pupper.

questions.title: What is the meaning of life?
questions.body: Great question, anon! The answer to life is found in your effort to catch your little tail. Woof!

questions.title: What is your favorite toy, Master Yochi?
questions.body: Great question, anon! My favorite toy is currently my Mozilla Firefox. He rolls, and he rolls, and he rolls. It is so much fun, I highly recommend to get your paws on one today!
